==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Parthian
<hw>Par"thi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
ancient Parthia, in Asia.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A native of
Parthia.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Parthian arrow</b></col>, <cd>an arrow discharged at an
enemy when retreating from him, as was the custom of the ancient
Parthians; hence, a parting shot.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>partial</ent>⟦br⟧
